                    during a practice session, suddenly realized they didn't know what 
                    project to work on. After some deliberation, they settled on creating a 
                    recipe website. The main goal of this site is to assist users in choosing
                    and preparing dishes. The team working on the project consists of two
                    members: Eivazly Ilkin and Nick Helmers. The creators poured their 
                    hearts and souls into this project, and they sincerely hope you will 
                    enjoy this application!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
